"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-04-parisolympics-kishane-thompson-oblique-seville-lead-qualifiers-100m-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"KINGSTON, Jamaica- Anticipation is building for what is expected to be an epic men's 100m final at the Olympic Games after the Jamaican pair of Kishane Thompson- 9.80 seconds (0.5m/s) and Oblique Seville who ran a personal best 9.81 seconds (0.7m/s) lead the qualifiers in the semi-finals at the Stade de France on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9152730468213177, \"rank\": 0.09256921271854236, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 1.5734614250927257e-12, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men won their respective heat, in relative ease, and will be hoping to return Jamaica to the heights of winning two medals in the event that was last achieved in London 12 years ago.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 407, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999995357551311, \"rank\": 3.0499968671420983e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9522645179409176, \"rank\": 0.05012594056507202, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {